| `Forrest Bao`_          |   forrest.bao [at] gmail.com        | VTK i/o, spectra port [1], MST fundi      |
+-------------------------+-------------------------------------+-------------------------------------------+
| `Joachim Giard`_        |   joachimgiard [at] gmail.com       | Surface shapes (depth, curvature) in C++  |
